printRequest.description: A JSON string containing the print request details. It must include 'printshops' (a list of print shop IDs) and 'files' (a map where each key is a filename and the value is an object containing a 'specs' list). Each spec object should include 'id' (printing schema ID), 'from' (starting page), and 'to' (ending page).

file.description: One or more PDF files to be printed. The filenames must match the keys provided in the 'files' map within the 'printRequest' JSON string.
